Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:33.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HD8CEBB&\blur2\3c&H21130C&}聽到馬戲團的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H7F6D65&\bord0}大家都歡喜雀躍加快著腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:40.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HDEBFA8&\blur2\3c&H87634E&}我也跟著要跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:44.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HFDF7F1&\bord0}儘管自己並沒有門票
