Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.73,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HD2DBE0&\bord0}默默地祈禱 僅僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:55.49,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H000000&\3c&HB6D7E1&\3a&H64&\blur1}我們總是碰撞傷痕累累
